---
import ViewTransitions from "astro/components/ViewTransitions.astro";
import "../styles/style.css";
---

<head>
   <ViewTransitions />
   <style>
      .hero-section {
         font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9fafb, #e2e8f0);
         padding: 60px 20px;
         text-align: center;
         animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
      }

      .hero-content {
         max-width: 800px;
         margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero-logo {
         width: 150px;
         margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .hero-title {
         font-size: 3rem;
         font-weight: bold;
         color: #333;
         margin-bottom: 20px;
         animation: textFadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .hero-description {
         font-size: 1.5rem;
         color: #555;
         margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .install-link {
         display: inline-block;
         padding: 10px 20px;
         background-color: #007bff;
         color: white;
         font-weight: bold;
         border-radius: 5px;
         text-decoration: none;
         transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .install-link:hover {
         background-color: #0056b3;
      }

      .footer-links {
         text-align: center;
         margin-top: 40px;
      }

      .footer-links a {
         color: #5433FF;
         margin: 0 10px;
         text-decoration: none;
         transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .footer-links a:hover {
         color: #3a1dff;
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
         from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
         to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      }

      @keyframes textFadeIn {
         from { opacity: 0; }
         to { opacity: 1; }
      }
   </style>
</head>

<main>
   <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-content">
         <img src="RiddleLogo_casual.png" alt="Riddle Logo" class="hero-logo" />
         <h1 class="hero-title">Riddle: クイズを作成し、挑戦しよう！</h1>
         <p class="hero-description">Riddleは、あなたの知識を試し、世界中の人々と共有するためのプラットフォームです。</p>
         <a href="https://riddle.app.link/3gWco6ifMMb" class="install-link">今すぐインストール</a>
         <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="/privacypolicy_riddle">privacy policy</a>
            <a href="/specialcommercialtransactionlaw_riddle">special commercial transaction law</a>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>
</main>
